F4A-42 — Complete Cycle
Outside all loops. Inside Prior Gates Incomplete → If No, AFTER Loop Active Applicability (sibling level — same indent as List Active Applicability For Cycle, Loop Active Applicability, etc.).
Dataverse → Update a row.

Table: Import Cycles
Row ID: fx → variables('varImportCycleID')
Status: Completed (dropdown)
Completed On: fx → utcNow()
Completed By: fx → concat('systemusers(', triggerOutputs()?['body/_modifiedby_value'], ')')

